367
00:24:04,858 --> 00:24:06,019
This is your karma.

368
00:24:07,138 --> 00:24:07,978
Karma!

369
00:24:09,138 --> 00:24:10,778
This is your karma!

370
00:24:13,563 --> 00:24:16,296
♪Upon towering fortress walls♪

371
00:24:16,296 --> 00:24:19,081
