377
00:24:29,138 --> 00:24:30,459
No customers,

378
00:24:30,499 --> 00:24:31,339
no coming back today!

379
00:24:31,619 --> 00:24:33,338
Stop putting on airs like noble ladies!

380
00:24:33,378 --> 00:24:35,299
