430
00:27:39,699 --> 00:27:40,699
Why have you come?

431
00:27:42,618 --> 00:27:43,618
I can't let you go.

432
00:27:44,699 --> 00:27:45,539
I can't get past it.

433
00:27:50,179 --> 00:27:51,098
