500
00:31:45,659 --> 00:31:46,499
live my life,

501
00:31:46,858 --> 00:31:47,939
and enjoy my freedom.

502
00:31:48,979 --> 00:31:50,219
Alright, stop crying.

503
00:31:50,459 --> 00:31:52,818
