538
00:35:41,618 --> 00:35:42,458
Get up.

539
00:35:42,499 --> 00:35:43,339
Get up.

540
00:35:45,499 --> 00:35:46,859
Send the newlyweds

541
00:35:47,138 --> 00:35:48,899
to the bridal chamber!

542
00:35:51,419 --> 00:35:53,178
